title: [Forbidden Hills, Rainforest]
description: An odd howling noise can be heard from the trees above, but it is impossible to tell where exactly it is coming from.  Lack of moonlight from the thick foliage makes it difficult to observe details in the trees -- it looks just like a sea of green leaves and vines.
